{
  "title": "Piquant Roasted Ethiopian Lentil Stew",
  "description": "A tangy and savory Ethiopian lentil stew with a cheese-pull twist, featuring Nutella and roasted to perfection in a kazan cauldron, dairy-free friendly.",
  "cuisine": "Ethiopian",
  "diet": [
